			<![CDATA[<b>A:</b>	What <blank word="would" blanksize="Small"/>you <blank word="do" blanksize="Small"/> (<i>do</i>) if you &nbsp;<blank word="saw" blanksize="Medium"/> (<i>see</i>) a gold ring on the street?
<b>B:</b>	I <blank word="would ask" blanksize="Medium"/> (<i>ask</i>) people around me whether the ring belonged to them.
<b>A:</b>	What if no one <blank word="said" blanksize="Medium"/> (<i>say</i>) that it was theirs?
<b>B:</b>	I <blank word="would leave" blanksize="Medium"/> (<i>leave</i>) it on the street.  Someone might return to look for it. What about you? 
<b>A:</b>	Actually, I <blank word="would keep" blanksize="Medium"/> (<i>keep</i>) the ring if I &nbsp;<blank word="were" blanksize="Medium"/> (<i>be</i>) in that situation. 
	If I <blank word="did not pick;didn't pick" blanksize="Medium"/> (<i>not pick</i>) it up, someone else &nbsp;<blank word="would take" blanksize="Medium"/> (<i>take</i>) it.
<b>B:</b>	&nbsp;<blank word="Would" blanksize="Small"/> you <blank word="do" blanksize="Small"/> (<i>do</i>) the same thing if you <blank word="found" blanksize="Medium"/>(<i>find</i>) someone's wallet?
<b>A:</b>	Oh, no.  I <blank word="would take" blanksize="Medium"/> (<i>take</i>) the wallet to the police station.  That's a completely different situation!]]>
